HEADWORD: Hordeolum
<hw>Hor*de"o*lum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. L.
<ets>hordeolus</ets>, dim. of <ets>hordeum</ets> barley.]</ety>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A small tumor upon the eyelid, resembling a grain
of barley; a sty.</def>⟦br⟧
